flash_blockchain/
│── blockchain.py        # Core blockchain logic (blocks, PoW, mining)
│── node.py              # Node API to handle transactions & networking
│── miner.py             # Mining script for solving PoW
│── wallet.py            # Wallet creation & key management
│── transaction.py       # Handles transactions (signing, validation)
│── server.py            # API for wallet, transactions, and blocks
│── explorer.py          # Blockchain explorer API
│── config.py            # Configuration settings (block time, difficulty)
│── utils.py             # Utility functions (hashing, signing)
│── requirements.txt     # Dependencies
│── frontend/            # (React-based blockchain explorer UI)
└── README.md            # Instructions